<div class="abh_box abh_box_up abh_box_drop-down"><ul class="abh_tabs"> <li class="abh_about abh_active"><a href="#abh_about">Author</a></li> <li class="abh_posts"><a href="#abh_posts">Recent Posts</a></li></ul><div class="abh_tab_content"><section class="vcard author abh_about_tab abh_tab" itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" style="display:block"><div class="abh_image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject"><a href="https://chacruna.net/author/jessica-rochester/" class="url" title="Rev. Dr. Jessica Rochester"> <img alt src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc869cf0a0006672fe01a7de4abdddf2?s=250&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g" srcset="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc869cf0a0006672fe01a7de4abdddf2?s=500&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g 2x" class="avatar avatar-250 photo" height="250" width="250" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></a > </div><div class="abh_social"> </div><div class="abh_text"><div class="abh_name fn name" itemprop="name" style="font-size:12px !important;"><a href="https://chacruna.net/author/jessica-rochester/" class="url">Rev. Dr. Jessica Rochester</a></div><div class="abh_job"></div><div class="description note abh_description" itemprop="description">Rev. Dr. Jessica Rochester is the Madrinha and President of Céu do Montréal, a Santo Daime Church she founded in 1997 in Montréal, Canada. She is an ordained Inter-Faith Minister with a Doctorate in Divinity. A Transpersonal counsellor, she trained in the work of Dr. Roberto Assagioli and trained with Dr. Stanislav Grof. </div></div> </section><section class="abh_posts_tab abh_tab"><div class="abh_image"><a href="https://chacruna.net/author/jessica-rochester/" class="url" title="Rev. Dr. Jessica Rochester"><img alt src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc869cf0a0006672fe01a7de4abdddf2?s=250&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g" srcset="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc869cf0a0006672fe01a7de4abdddf2?s=500&#038;d=blank&#038;r=g 2x" class="avatar avatar-250 photo" height="250" width="250" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></a></div><div class="abh_social"> </div><div class="abh_text"><div class="abh_name" style="font-size:12px !important;">Latest posts by Rev. Dr. Jessica Rochester <span class="abh_allposts">(<a href="https://chacruna.net/author/jessica-rochester/">see all</a>)</span></div><div class="abh_description note"><ul> <li> <a href="https://chacruna.net/how-ayahuasca-church-received-religious-exemption-canada/">How Our Santo Daime Church Received Religious Exemption to Use Ayahuasca in Canada</a><span> &#8211; July 17, 2017</span> </li></ul></div></div> </section></div> </div><div id="tdi_6" class="tdc-row"><div class="vc_row tdi_7  wpb_row td-pb-row">
