<header class="td-post-title">
<ul class="td-category"><li class="entry-category"><a href="https://chacruna.net/category/policy/">Policy</a></li></ul> <h1 class="entry-title">How Our Santo Daime Church Received Religious Exemption to Use Ayahuasca in Canada</h1>
<div class="td-module-meta-info">
<span class="td-post-date"><time class="entry-date updated td-module-date" datetime="2017-07-17T10:01:35-05:00">July 17, 2017</time></span> </div>
</header>
</div>
</div>
</div>
