<h3 class="entry-title td-module-title"><a href="https://chacruna.net/psychedelic-judaism/" rel="bookmark" title="Psychonautic Judaism: The Psychedelic Renaissance and the Future of Judaism">Psychonautic Judaism: The Psychedelic Renaissance and the Future of Judaism</a></h3>
<p> <span class="td-post-author-name"><a href="https://chacruna.net/author/chacruna-institute-for-plant-medicines/">Chacruna Institute</a> <span>-</span> </span> <span class="td-post-date"><time class="entry-date updated td-module-date" datetime="2021-05-25T13:51:41-05:00">May 25, 2021</time></span> </div></div></div>
<div class="td-excerpt">
<p>Wednesday, June 9th, 2021 from 12-1:30pm PST</p>
<p>REGISTER FOR THIS EVENT HERE</p>
<p>There is growing enthusiasm in Jewish communities about possible ancient use and modern applications of plant medicine in Jewish spiritual development. &nbsp;Psychedelic Judaism introduce new potential modes of &nbsp;healing...</p>
